{"tid":85811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家支持修哥繼續追擊揪出Ben哥背後啲團隊","createTime":"2017-01-18T15:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T22:11:55.000Z","uid":38539,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"201a20d86eb2471f7357d650b1ce53f68dd43c94","tid":85811,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"孔曰成仁 孟曰取義<br />\n今次修哥站出來 決定繼續追擊 不在輸贏 在氣節<br />\nBen哥背後團隊(我稱為Z) 於FB開戶自稱Ben哥發文<br />\n實際操控住Ben 利用細佬仔作商品賺錢 專橫跋扈 <br />\n今次如果修哥投降 Z必定沾沾自喜 變本加利<br />\n咁個班咁笑柒修哥啲人咪姐係等於助紂為孽？<br />\n<br />\n游學修略算知名藝人，今次仍冒險發聲，若不成功那是天意，<br />\n點能夠向惡勢力屈服認低威？<br />\n如果今次修哥和連登仔選擇投降，只會終身羞恥，是問各位顏面何存？"},{"pid":"b86da4986fdba66c49caa0c87c791b33cf50314e","tid":85811,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaa1269a316732ac710610e88f29218d384d29a1","tid":85811,"uid":5293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"件事可以同關家姐比，一樣咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8514dfab149db703ed59460ecd1b55c430f7932f","tid":85811,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b0e1522707ec3649301af2d1d2c3fa19a75e4a9","tid":85811,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4034d74e655e9350153a15787998b89e7d136312","tid":85811,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"邵"},{"pid":"c21624b752d162b2d70a24c3221f44f9a2900959","tid":85811,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0efcd1809b2af0a1ed5ea32957b6121e04f8dc08","tid":85811,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:42:47.